
  Drakloak    Dragon Type Pokémon

  It’s capable of flying faster 
  than 120 mph.  It battles alongside 
  Dreepy and dotes on them until 
  they successfully evolve. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Dreepy ► Drakloak ► Dragapult

